{"tid":1155614,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2020東京奧運門票預售安排","createTime":"2019-05-15T05:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T02:24:37.000Z","uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3271ce5130f16e01147b9a75ed183b3446d534b6","tid":1155614,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:15:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkolympic.org/articles_detail.php?cid=20&amp;id=3221&amp;language=tc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkolympic.org%2Farticles_detail.php%3Fcid%3D20%26id%3D3221%26language%3Dtc&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=5288cf0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkolympic.org/articles_detail.php?cid=20&amp;id=3221&amp;language=tc</a><br />\n<br />\n2020年東京奧運 &ndash; 門票安排<br />\n25.04.2019 <br />\n2020年東京奧運組委會(組委會)已於4月18日公佈有關獲取2020年東京奧運門票的抽選活動程序(<a href=\"https://tokyo2020.org/en/news/notice/20190418-01.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftokyo2020.org%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fnotice%2F20190418-01.html&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=12615031\" target=\"_blank\">https://tokyo2020.org/en/news/notice/20190418-01.html</a>)，現階段此項抽選門票活動只適用於日本居民，在日本的外國旅客並不適用。常居日本境外的旅客或居民，需向其居住地區的地區奧委會或票務代理訂購門票。詳情可瀏覧2020年東京奧運門票官方網站<a href=\"https://ticket.tokyo2020.org/?culture=en-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fticket.tokyo2020.org%2F%3Fculture%3Den-us&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=c3b1d974\" target=\"_blank\">https://ticket.tokyo2020.org/?culture=en-us</a>。 <br />\n<br />\n至於在香港的門票銷售，本會很高興已委任香港中國旅行社有限公司(香港中旅社)為香港區的票務代理。有關門票銷售的詳情，包括銷售日期、價格等，將適時公佈。 <br />\n請密切瀏覧香港中旅社的網站<a href=\"http://www.ctshk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctshk.com&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=4b66ec3d\" target=\"_blank\">www.ctshk.com</a>。有關門票的銷售詳情，將會在此發佈。 <br />\n<br />\n發稿機構：中國香港體育協會暨奧林匹克委員會 <br />\n發稿日期：2019年4月25 日"},{"pid":"e89fd8cb6568a6bd7176cb1c504db998f5ef1ad2","tid":1155614,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"呢篇嘢先係用嚟教壞人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Japan_Living/M.1557814692.A.7C1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FJapan_Living%2FM.1557814692.A.7C1.html&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=1eaba6cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Japan_Living/M.1557814692.A.7C1.html</a>"},{"pid":"d19109f87b814cb4ad59796921f4cd6682a5fa39","tid":1155614,"uid":19762,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"・日本國內以官方網站為唯一購票途徑(<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日本IP</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n・官網購票需要登入ID帳號(免費申請，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">需日本電話</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />及地址)<br />\n・第一階段購票申請為 5/9~5/28 (抽籤)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：易搞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：難搞，不過搞得掂嘅就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3655a008dabf72b4fdb1a6b2082c038fdacb50b3","tid":1155614,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"想快d知到時賽事門票幾錢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e70157b945e4a4aa3dfe0a05191e4025174668","tid":1155614,"uid":134226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3655a008dabf72b4fdb1a6b2082c038fdacb50b3","tid":1155614,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"想快d知到時賽事門票幾錢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ticket.tokyo2020.or